Generic Targets:
   noargs|all|help|targets Print this text and exit
   usage                   Print more detailed information on each target
Global Building Targets:
   all_freebsd             Build all packages
   depend_freebsd          Perform `make depend' for all packages
   forcedepend_freebsd     Perform `make forcedepend' for all packages
Global Maintenance Targets:
   clean_freebsd           Perform `make clean' for all packags
   distclean_freebsd       Perform `make distclean' for all packages
   pull_freebsd            Perform `make pull' for all packages
   commit_freebsd          Perform `make commit' for all packages
Git Maintenance Targets:
   pull                    An alias to `git pull'
   tag_freebsd             Perform `make tag' for all packages
   forcetag_freebsd        Perform `make forcetag' for all packages
   taglist_freebsd         Perform `make taglist' for all packages
Git Addition Targets:
   import                  Import current working directory to git
   commit                  An alias to `git commit'
